# Every gate is false by default. Plan the organization guardrail and its
# temporary Policy Admin lease first. Then create only the project in a complete
# saved plan by enabling production project creation; keep that gate true
# thereafter. Attest project creation only after verifying its ID, number, sole
# expected creator Owner, and absence of Editor. Enable the remaining project
# bootstrap in a later complete saved plan so every authorization expression is
# known and inspectable. Create and verify the gateway exception in its separate
# temporary project Policy Admin phase before the foundation, Owner removal, and
# CI handoff.
